<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٢١٨ - مَعْمَرٌ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{بِجَانِبِ الْغَرْبِيِّ}</span> <span class="c4">[القصص: ٤٤]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«يَعْنِي جَبَلًا غَرْبِيًّا كَانَ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>